    "name": {
      "zh": "麦克米兰 A5 枪托，适配雷明顿700长枪机版本（橄榄色）",
      "en": "McMillan A5 stock for Remington 700 long action (ODG)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "McMillan",
      "en": "McMillan A5"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "A-5枪托整合了所有A系列每个产品中最受欢迎的特性，打造出了这款款专业战术步枪枪托。相比我们其他A系列枪托，A-5采用更宽更平的河狸尾式前护木，枪机与枪管位置更低以提升稳定性，并配备紧凑型手枪握把。橄榄褐色版本。",
      "en": "The A-5 stock combines all the most requested features of the entire A-series into one professional tactical rifle stock. Compared to our other A-series stocks, the A-5 uses a beavertail forearm that is wider and flatter. The action and barrel sit lower for enhanced stability. The A-5 uses a trim pistol grip."
    },
